{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":301601,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"Phew... I was able to return the handkerchief...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301601,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"It feels like...I understand less and less now."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":801100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Then we can still get married,@we'll just live separately.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(...Loving each other even when you aren't@together... Can you still be happy that way?)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(But, if you're a family, a couple,@shouldn't you live together?)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":801100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"I want to become a family with you, because right@now we're just strangers in the eyes of the world.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"(...Sure enough, no matter how much you like each@other, until marriage you're effectively strangers.)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(Thinking about it that way, is marriage...)"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(...just a means for strangers@to be considered a family...?)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801100,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":801100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"...And I want to be the place you can call home.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":801100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"The family that heals you after@a long day of hard work."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(A place to call home...)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(I wonder if that's what it means...to be a family...)"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(...They say it's different for everyone...@But what does it really mean?)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":301601}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51193_tower_masara_kokoro/memoria_1908_1.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"Even though it's already evening,@there's quite a few people here...","narrationCoverOpacity":100.0,"narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"An old man walking his dog,@a mother looking after her excited child,@someone sitting alone watching the waves,@a couple of friends chatting together,@an elderly coupling walking along the shore..."},{"narration":"Are all these people happy?@What even is happiness...?"},{"narration":"Will I be happy if I get married?@Will I be happy if I have kids?@Will I be happy if I'm alone?@Will I be happy if I'm together with someone?"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(...Any time I try to make sense of it,@I feel like I understand even less...)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(Maybe the reason for that is...)"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"(Because my idea of happiness@has always been \"that day\"...)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_19071.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"promist"},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20256.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301601,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"Happiness...@That was happiness, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"...Somehow, I'm not even sure of that anymore."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301601,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:7106_telmail]*Jingle*","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"...Oh, a news notification."},{"bgm":"stop","nameNarration":"","narration":"【BREAKING NEWS】@A woman in her twenties has been arrested@on suspicion of attempted assault.@The cause seems to be related to a@previous relationship...","narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":180.0},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301601,"pos":1}],"narration":"【EXCLUSIVE SCOOP!】@The latest news of the couple reported@to be having an affair! "},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301601,"motion":100,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","narrationEffect":"out","surround":"7025_wave","textCenter":"...*Sigh*@I wonder..."},{"chara":[{"id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301601,"motion":200,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kokoro","textCenter":"Love...marriage..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"black","surround":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kokoro","narration":"Family, love, marriage, and all that...@I thought it was something filled with happiness.@Or maybe I just wanted it to be that way...","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"Maybe I was just being that naive,@and this whole time it's been@something vague and foolish...@I wonder..."},{"narration":"This thought, even though@I should be devastated by it...@I can't deny it."},{"narration":"Ah, this is the worst..."},{"narration":"...Masara, what would you say@at a time like this...?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}